msgctxt "56_Kiryu"
msgid "You're the boss of the Purple Killers?"
msgstr "You're the boss of the Purple Killers?"

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "68_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "I really do love bowling. A single attacker strikes down 10 opponents. It's as if I'm witnessing a perfect example of marksmanship."
msgstr "Me encantan los bolos, de verdad. Un solo tiro y ¡paf!, abajo los 10 pinos. Parece como si viera un ejemplo perfecto de puntería."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "80_Kiryu"
msgid "Let's settle this, once and for all."
msgstr "...Oye, terminemos con esto de una vez."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "92_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "That direct manner of yours... I can see that you're accustomed to facing matters head on."
msgstr "Con esa forma de hablar tan directa... Se ve que no le tienes miedo a nada."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "104_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "One never knows when death will come, yet you won't even allow me the simple pleasure of watching people bowl?"
msgstr "Es curioso que, sabiendo que la muerte acecha a cada instante, tú no me des ni siquiera el tiempo para disfrutar de un partido de bolos..."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "116_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "Oh well, it's all the same. If you insist on rushing headlong into death, I'll give you that which you seek."
msgstr "Está bien, como quieras. Si insistes en correr al encuentro de la muerte, te daré lo que buscas."

#. y4:line_status=translated
msgctxt "128_Purple Killers Boss"
msgid "Let's begin."
msgstr "Comencemos."

